  20 Jul 2002; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> yaboot-1.3.6.ebuild :
  Adjusted keywords

  14 Jul 2002; phoen][x <phoenix@gentoo.org> yaboot-1.3.6.ebuild :
  Added LICENSE, KEYWORDS, SLOT.

